{"tid":1977784,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【選陳國師有撚量水送 智商190up先睇得明（好似係），未食藥系列】陳雲：好多朋友以為我會出來參選，或者勸我出來參選","createTime":"2020-04-18T08:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T04:39:08.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"560bb1239d5c01206b2cfe4a4d1e4f9b2a1ebeb0","tid":1977784,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDJKAGA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDJKAGA.gif&h=2e15129c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：好多朋友以為我會出來參選，或者勸我出來參選。各位，請回吧，省一點吧。<br />\n我在2016年的選舉已經講得好清楚，我是為了香港修憲、永續自治的議程參選的，而即使選到了，也可能會因為推進這個議程而五區請辭，請辭之後無法重選，故此我只是為議程參選，並不是為了做議員而參選。<br />\n2016年是香港修憲自治的唯一機會，因為當年是中美友好的最後一年。之後特朗普上台，逆轉了中美關係，目前的武漢肺炎更被特朗普總統騎劫，借助來做全球封城，逼使西方國家貿易脫華（decouple China）。即使中共現在自行修憲，令香港自治，也得不到國際社會的祝福。<br />\n所謂時機，就是這樣。從1997至2047，香港只有一次拯救的機會，這個機會，由陳雲親手策劃，由香港人自己親手糟蹋。<br />\n所以話，陳雲會不會參加選舉呢？泛民認為會囉，因為我的生計又開始被破壞了，重複2015-16年的情況。不過我這次已經無公職或教席可以給泛民弄丟，最後一個專欄都在四月中丟失啦。泛民要搞我，就得返一間破廟可以搞囉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvE54zR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvE54zR.jpg&h=b9967a26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/18/1fJLlS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F18%2F1fJLlS.png&h=1eda4ee0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16285918cd915a2d6335c880ad4ea5ebd77bde72","tid":1977784,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M87K7QM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM87K7QM.jpg&h=36c15758&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd9d434b8fdb1b302fce353c6f1bdf6aa49e7cf7","tid":1977784,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"平生不買銀離子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n稱國師粉也枉然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ce949d0064514f19c208ffba4ea23b1a070d08","tid":1977784,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"加個智力門鑑, 又撚到佢班信徒覺得自己係少數睇穿真相既智者"},{"pid":"edc443fe0bfcd7d6fd730e03d10321598dc42acb","tid":1977784,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e1ce949d0064514f19c208ffba4ea23b1a070d08","tid":1977784,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"加個智力門鑑, 又撚到佢班信徒覺得自己係少數睇穿真相既智者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cdad07f4676da7ab6d48eb25141bcc04dd0e0a","tid":1977784,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd9d434b8fdb1b302fce353c6f1bdf6aa49e7cf7","tid":1977784,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"平生不買銀離子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n稱國師粉也枉然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb6f711bf4a0384afead7fcada2ac7d9910b430","tid":1977784,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/18/1fJLlS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h